I submit these Control to the Perl community in the hope that someone
other than myself will find them useful. I have placed POD documentation
with example program.

Requirements :-

        Tk              - 800.005 or above

The suite is built/installed in the conventional manner :-

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make install

Bugs, suggestions, fixes, etc. can either be sent to palash_bksys@yahoo.com

